A chocolate cake made with the finest ingredients
and crafted with utmost skill.
A masterpiece that fills the air with the
enchanting aroma of cocoa.

column3:
とろけるように甘いハニーケーキ

黄色い生地は心を弾ませる逸品
column4:
A honey cake that is irresistibly sweet, like
melting away.
Although it appears simple, it is rich in flavor
and moist.
The yellow batter is a masterpiece that makes
hearts leap with joy.

column3:
一口サイズの小さなマフィン
中にガライモのペーストが入っていて、食べると
体力とスタミナが回復する
column4:
A small muffin the size of a bite.
It contains a paste made from Gala potato, and
when you eat it, your health and stamina will
recover.

column3:
見た目にも癒される愛らしい形のウエハース
優しく軽やかな味わいで、食べると
体力が回復する
column4:
A charming wafer with an adorable appearance that
brings healing even to the eyes.
With a gentle and light flavor, when consumed, it
replenishes your Health Points.

column3:
様々な果物やナッツが練り込まれた黒いヌガー
一口ごとに変わる味わいで、食べると
スタミナが回復する
column4:
Black nougat infused with various fruits and nuts.
With each bite, the flavor changes and when
consumed, it restores stamina.

column3:
キラキラ光る大きな雪の結晶
口に入れるとすっと溶け、爽やかな甘味で
体力とスタミナが回復する
column4:
A sparkling, large snowflake that shines
brightly.
When you put it in your mouth, it melts
instantly, providing a refreshing sweetness.
It restores your Health Points and Stamina.
